        "Intensively stimulates and massages all abdominal organs including the liver, kidneys, pancreas, spleen, and intestines through prolonged compression, promoting optimal digestive function and natural detoxification processes",
        "Maximizes spinal flexibility and mobility through progressive vertebral articulation enhanced by the strong pulling action of the interlaced hands, benefiting those with spinal stiffness or compression",
        "Develops exceptional hamstring elasticity and length through the sustained, deep stretching facilitated by the secure foot grip, helping prevent injury and improve athletic performance",
        "Enhances proprioceptive awareness and bilateral coordination through the complex finger interlacing pattern that requires precise hand positioning and balanced muscular engagement",
        "Provides profound therapeutic benefits for anxiety, depression, and mental fatigue through the deeply introspective nature of the pose combined with calming parasympathetic nervous system activation",
